# KairOS Vault Rules

This is a **personal knowledge vault**, not a software project.
KairOS engine code (skills, hooks, templates) lives in a separate repo.

## You may edit

- Markdown content files: `inbox/`, `daily/`, `projects/`, `reference/`
- GTD lists: `next-actions.md`, `waiting-for.md`, `someday-maybe.md`
- Profile: `profile.md`

## Do NOT edit or delete

- Dotfiles and dotdirectories: `.cursor/`, `.claude/`, `.cline/`, `.gitignore`,
  `.engine-root`, `.engine-remote`, `.engine-branch`, `.clinerules`
- Anything under `_kair/` — engine-synced; changes will be overwritten on `/kair-update`

## Engine changes

If a skill, hook, or template needs to change, do not edit `_kair/`.
Say: **"This requires a KairOS engine update — open the engine repo."**
